{"tid":419809,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"海外居住嘅巴絲你哋有冇覺得自己中文有退步？","createTime":"2017-09-30T19:33:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-08T01:27:21.000Z","uid":28802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"0f2ce0f51630a1183da94992c4ea168005a9b906","tid":419809,"uid":28802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T19:33:11.000Z","msg":"早幾日同個LA番嚟嘅朋友見面<br />\n小學同學嚟過咗去美國都成七年<br />\n最近番嚟香港又有小學re-u咁就見到佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢中三過去讀中學 啱啱u grad 番嚟香港做嘢<br />\n佢話雖然同親戚住但佢好多中文字都已經唔記得晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同佢基本講嘢係冇問題嘅<br />\n佢亦都話讀中文字仲ok 不過打中文嘅話會用粵拼<br />\n<br />\n有冇喺海外嘅巴絲可以講吓你哋點樣去維繫自己嘅中文<br />\n過咗去外國耐一排會唔會覺得有退步<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4252a6ec7830349329d27281040a2d8df5a561b","tid":419809,"uid":28802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T19:33:20.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"b85d2468b916f61ee0a75e4e42445507b9156ce6","tid":419809,"uid":140727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T22:43:16.000Z","msg":"仲識講 打字都係用粵拼<br />\n一寫字有啲要諗好耐 部首嗰啲方向會掉轉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"610e9d2d792979b577c8f4fd588a5466ad27be99","tid":419809,"uid":37730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T22:48:34.000Z","msg":"睇同講完全無問題<br />\n但寫d少用既字可能要諗一諗"},{"pid":"b43c4e834906bb0dda6da82fe97041b11a550bae","tid":419809,"uid":66769,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T22:50:54.000Z","msg":"我會，英文唔見好左，但係中文表達就差左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7df29993a21a8fe81165c648139a73fa7be87793","tid":419809,"uid":54344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T22:52:26.000Z","msg":"有啲字真係諗唔起，要問老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其他聽